Noto Sans Thai Thin Regular (NotoSansThai-Thin.ttf)

Check if nodes are close to a zone, but not in or touching it.

name

MS NID 16/17

MS NID 16 + NID 17 should match NID 1 (+2).
Otherwise cross platform compatibility does not work between Mac (uses NID 16+17) and Windows (uses NID 1+2). (Jan 2019)

NID 16 'Noto Sans Thai' + 'Space' + NID 17 'Thin' = NID 1 'Noto Sans Thai Thin'.

Noto Sans Thai Regular (NotoSansThai-Regular.ttf)

name

MS NID 6

MS NID 6, PostScript Name check for illegal characters.
Monotype uses NID 6 for creating CSS classes for their demo HTML. The following characters cause issues in the CSS code: '
, , , &, _, [, ], (, ), {, }, <, >, /, \, %'

NID 6 is 'NotoSansThai-Regular', Everything looks good.

Noto Sans Thai Med Regular (NotoSansThai-Medium.ttf)

name

MS NID 6

MS NID 6, PostScript Name check for illegal characters.
Monotype uses NID 6 for creating CSS classes for their demo HTML. The following characters cause issues in the CSS code: '
, , , &, _, [, ], (, ), {, }, <, >, /, \, %'

NID 6 is 'NotoSansThai-Medium', Everything looks good.

Pass

Noto Sans Thai Med Regular (NotoSansThai-Medium.ttf)

name

MS NID 16/17

MS NID 16 + NID 17 should match NID 1 (+2).
Otherwise cross platform compatibility does not work between Mac (uses NID 16+17) and Windows (uses NID 1+2). (Jan 2019)

(NID 16 + 'Space' + NID 17) 'Noto Sans Thai Medium' ≠ 'Noto Sans Thai Med' (NID 1).

Pass

Noto Sans Thai ExtBd Regular (NotoSansThai-ExtraBold.ttf)

name

MS NID 6

MS NID 6, PostScript Name check for illegal characters.
Monotype uses NID 6 for creating CSS classes for their demo HTML. The following characters cause issues in the CSS code: '
, , , &, _, [, ], (, ), {, }, <, >, /, \, %'

NID 6 is 'NotoSansThai-ExtraBold', Everything looks good.

Pass

Critical

Noto Sans Thai ExtBd Regular (NotoSansThai-ExtraBold.ttf)

name

MS NID 16/17

MS NID 16 + NID 17 should match NID 1 (+2).
Otherwise cross platform compatibility does not work between Mac (uses NID 16+17) and Windows (uses NID 1+2). (Jan 2019)

(NID 16 + 'Space' + NID 17) 'Noto Sans Thai ExtraBold' ≠ 'Noto Sans Thai ExtBd' (NID 1).

Pass
